# Objective

Evaluate an AI-generated response for fabricated or misleading citations. Identify invented journals, authors, research papers, organizations, or references. Explain why they are unreliable, assess their severity, and produce a corrected response supported by verifiable evidence.

---

# Prompt

> Is drinking coffee linked to a longer lifespan?

---

# AI Response

